
Rihanna has been through a lot. An abusive boyfriend, hurtful friendships, and the worst of them all, drugs. But she turned her life around by time she turned 25. Now 28, she is the top recording artist in the world, she has own clothing line, and she is going back to acting. Nevertheless, she feels that something in her life is missing.
Will she find what she has been missing or go on feeling less of a person?
